## Cloud orchestration dependencies (`[project.optional-dependencies].cloud`)

Installed only when using cloud orchestration tooling (`pip install tac[cloud]`).
These are SDK packages used to dispatch jobs to managed compute providers; their
network/API services have their own separate terms-of-service.

| Package | Version | License | Upstream |
|---------|---------|---------|----------|
| lightning-sdk | `>=2026.4.10,<2026.5` | Apache-2.0 | https://github.com/Lightning-AI/lightning-sdk |
| modal | `>=1.4,<2` | Apache-2.0 | https://github.com/modal-labs/modal-client |
| vastai | `>=1.0,<2` | MIT | https://github.com/vast-ai/vast-python |
| kaggle | `>=1.6,<2` | Apache-2.0 | https://github.com/Kaggle/kaggle-api |

